<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 00:31:00 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列司法监察员称高等法院法官卡布行为不道德</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/israels-judiciary-ombudsman-says-high-court-justice-kabub-acted-unethically/0000018e-816f-df27-adee-a7ff198c0000</link><description>监察员裁定，查立德·卡布 (Chaled Kabub) 法官未经授权接受媒体采访，违反了法官道德准则，并驳回了卡布 (Kabub) 对他参与涉及其子女的法律纠纷审判的指控的回应。所有针对他的投诉均由右翼活动家谢伊·格利克（Shay Glick）提交</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 20:20:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/israels-judiciary-ombudsman-says-high-court-justice-kabub-acted-unethically/0000018e-816f-df27-adee-a7ff198c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列总检察长反对内塔尼亚胡政府试图延长哈雷迪法案草案的最后期限</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/israeli-ag-opposes-netanyahu-govts-attempt-to-extend-deadline-on-haredi-draft-bill/0000018e-816c-df27-adee-a7feb2b10000</link><description>提交请求的截止日期是周三午夜。如果不提交，内阁关于免除极端正统派男子征兵的决定将于周一到期，他们将被征召服兵役</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 20:06:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/israeli-ag-opposes-netanyahu-govts-attempt-to-extend-deadline-on-haredi-draft-bill/0000018e-816c-df27-adee-a7feb2b10000</guid></item><item><title>正统派兵役豁免危机对以色列政治来说是一个地震事件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/the-haredi-exemptions-law-crisis-will-draw-israels-political-lines-for-a-generation/0000018e-815b-ddea-a1de-835f4b900000</link><description>即使本杰明·内塔尼亚胡未能通过一项免除所有犹太学院学生服兵役的法律，极端正统派政党也可能会留在政府，但在下一次选举后，他们可能会长期处于反对派状态</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 19:56:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/the-haredi-exemptions-law-crisis-will-draw-israels-political-lines-for-a-generation/0000018e-815b-ddea-a1de-835f4b900000</guid></item><item><title>“压迫越多，以色列的年轻阿拉伯人就越强调他们的巴勒斯坦身份”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-03-27/ty-article-podcast/the-more-oppression-there-is-the-more-younger-arabs-in-israel-identify-as-palestinians/0000018e-8071-d861-adff-ce7d3b6b0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 19:23:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-03-27/ty-article-podcast/the-more-oppression-there-is-the-more-younger-arabs-in-israel-identify-as-palestinians/0000018e-8071-d861-adff-ce7d3b6b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵在加沙南部战斗中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/israeli-soldier-killed-in-southern-gaza-combat/0000018e-8107-d0d3-a98e-d7ff33930000</link><description>参谋军士。 21 岁的尼西姆·卡奇隆 (Nisim Kachlon) 来自哈德拉 (Hadera)，在加沙地带南部与恐怖分子的战斗中身亡</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 18:09:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/israeli-soldier-killed-in-southern-gaza-combat/0000018e-8107-d0d3-a98e-d7ff33930000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 173 天：据报道内塔尼亚胡寻求重新安排他取消的 DC 会议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-173-netanyahu-reportedly-trying-to-reschedule-d-c-he-just-canceled/0000018e-80f6-d0d3-a98e-d6ff2b800000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡表示，他取消了华盛顿特区的代表团，以“向哈马斯传递信息” ■ 在华盛顿特区，国防部长加兰特表示，战后以色列和哈马斯都不会统治加沙，必须建立当地的替代方案 ■ 以色列人在黎巴嫩猛烈火箭弹袭击后丧生 ■ 爱尔兰表示将干预南非针对以色列的种族灭绝案 ■ 哈马斯公布了据称是军事首领穆罕默德·代夫的录音 ■ 这是战争开始 173 天后您需要了解的内容</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 17:35:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-173-netanyahu-reportedly-trying-to-reschedule-d-c-he-just-canceled/0000018e-80f6-d0d3-a98e-d6ff2b800000</guid></item><item><title>为什么这个女人必须将拉比告上以色列最高法院离婚</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/why-this-woman-had-to-take-the-rabbinate-to-israels-supreme-court-to-get-a-divorce/0000018e-806b-d719-a5ae-ac7b25970000</link><description>在一场涉及三个独立法庭的战斗中，维塔·罗森伯格终于获得了胜利。问题不在于丈夫的顽抗，而在于以色列的首席拉比，后者要求她证明自己的犹太身份才能获得宗教离婚</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 17:19:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/why-this-woman-had-to-take-the-rabbinate-to-israels-supreme-court-to-get-a-divorce/0000018e-806b-d719-a5ae-ac7b25970000</guid></item><item><title>警察搜查参加反政府抗议的以色列人的卧室</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/police-ransack-bedroom-of-israeli-who-participated-in-anti-govt-protest/0000018e-80a5-d5aa-abdf-f9bf188b0000</link><description>警方在房间里捣毁后没有找到他们要找的东西，但最终逮捕了这名活动人士，并试图将她拘留五天。 “我们作为激进主义的行动空间正在缩小，”她说</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 17:19:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/police-ransack-bedroom-of-israeli-who-participated-in-anti-govt-protest/0000018e-80a5-d5aa-abdf-f9bf188b0000</guid></item><item><title>白宫：内塔尼亚胡决定“重新安排”以色列代表团赴美参与拉法行动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-says-he-pulled-israels-delegation-to-u-s-to-send-a-message-to-hamas/0000018e-8084-d49b-a3bf-f49f81230000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡似乎推翻了之前的声明，即在美国决定不否决联合国安理会停火决议后，他将以色列代表团撤回华盛顿，以此向哈马斯发出“信息”，即它不能依赖国际压力</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 16:09:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-says-he-pulled-israels-delegation-to-u-s-to-send-a-message-to-hamas/0000018e-8084-d49b-a3bf-f49f81230000</guid></item><item><title>以色列裔美国经济学家、诺贝尔奖获得者丹尼尔·卡尼曼去世，享年 90 岁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/israeli-american-economist-and-nobel-laureate-daniel-kahneman-dies-at-90/0000018e-8094-d113-a1ce-9a97ccc10000</link><description>卡尼曼与阿莫斯·特沃斯基联合开展的将心理学见解融入经济学的开创性工作为他赢得了 2002 年诺贝尔奖。他是内塔尼亚胡政府司法改革的直言不讳的批评者</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 15:47:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/israeli-american-economist-and-nobel-laureate-daniel-kahneman-dies-at-90/0000018e-8094-d113-a1ce-9a97ccc10000</guid></item><item><title>被停职的以色列政府发言人埃隆·利维正式被解雇</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/suspended-israeli-government-spokesman-eylon-levy-officially-dismissed/0000018e-803d-de8e-adae-acfd6d5f0000</link><description>在与英国外交部长发生推特争议后，一名政府官员表示，利维“偏离了以色列的信息，采取了太多自由”</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 15:13:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/suspended-israeli-government-spokesman-eylon-levy-officially-dismissed/0000018e-803d-de8e-adae-acfd6d5f0000</guid></item><item><title>在加沙受伤的以色列歌手拒绝点燃独立日火炬</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/israeli-singer-wounded-in-gaza-refuses-to-light-ceremonial-independence-day-torch/0000018e-8000-dc05-abef-abc9de140000</link><description>演员、歌手兼以色列国防军预备役军人伊丹·阿梅迪拒绝了这一请求，称其他人比他更值得，他希望“由于我写的文字而不是战争英雄主义，他将获得点燃火炬的功绩”</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 15:00:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/israeli-singer-wounded-in-gaza-refuses-to-light-ceremonial-independence-day-torch/0000018e-8000-dc05-abef-abc9de140000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡预计将请求以色列高等法院延长哈雷迪法案草案的期限</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-expected-to-ask-israels-high-court-for-extension-over-haredi-draft-bill/0000018e-7fe3-d669-a9fe-7fef35dc0000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡向其联盟中的极端正统派领导人保证，政府对犹太学校的资助不会受到影响，因为这是一项可以免除所有正统派男子应征入伍的法案谈判的一部分。然而，尚不清楚总理如何证明这一点</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 14:56:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-expected-to-ask-israels-high-court-for-extension-over-haredi-draft-bill/0000018e-7fe3-d669-a9fe-7fef35dc0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军袭击黎巴嫩造成七人死亡后，以色列人在以色列北部发射的重型火箭弹中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/israeli-killed-in-rocket-barrage-fired-at-northern-israel-after-idf-strikes-in-lebanon/0000018e-7eed-d9f5-a7ae-7eedc2f60000</link><description>来自以色列北部德鲁兹村庄的扎赫尔·比沙拉 (Zaher Bishara) 在真主党向什莫纳镇发射约 30 枚火箭弹后在一栋工业建筑中身亡。此次袭击是对以色列对黎巴嫩发动袭击的报复，该袭击造成七人死亡</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 13:47:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/israeli-killed-in-rocket-barrage-fired-at-northern-israel-after-idf-strikes-in-lebanon/0000018e-7eed-d9f5-a7ae-7eedc2f60000</guid></item><item><title>解释：谁是犹太极端正统派亲巴勒斯坦活动家 Neturei Karta</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/explained-who-are-neturei-karta-the-jewish-ultra-orthodox-pro-palestinian-activists/0000018e-7039-df85-afde-f77d40640000</link><description>在网上和街头，这些激烈反犹太复国主义的极端正统犹太活动分子对他们完全回归《托拉法》的独裁目标以及对哈马斯、伊朗和真主党的拥抱保持沉默。目前，他们的“停止加沙迫害”信息在美国进步示威活动中受到热烈欢迎</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 13:18:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/explained-who-are-neturei-karta-the-jewish-ultra-orthodox-pro-palestinian-activists/0000018e-7039-df85-afde-f77d40640000</guid></item><item><title>我们以色列母亲必须从我们的领导人手中拯救我们的孩子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-03-27/ty-article-opinion/.premium/we-israeli-mothers-must-save-our-children-from-our-leaders/0000018e-7581-d637-abbf-f7895a6d0000</link><description>我已经被有一天在另一场战争中失去我的儿子的恐惧所压倒，而这场战争是我们具有弥赛亚思想的政府搞砸的，他们更喜欢神奇的思考而不是建设一个可行的未来。现在比以往任何时候都更加紧迫：我们以色列人民必须将他们驱逐出去</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 12:54:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-03-27/ty-article-opinion/.premium/we-israeli-mothers-must-save-our-children-from-our-leaders/0000018e-7581-d637-abbf-f7895a6d0000</guid></item><item><title>四名巴勒斯坦人在约旦河西岸被以色列军队杀害，其中三人是在空袭中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/three-palestinians-killed-by-israeli-army-in-west-bank-two-of-them-in-airstrike/0000018e-7f52-d680-a1cf-ff57e8d30000</link><description>以色列国防军宣布，周三，两名武装男子在杰宁的一次空袭中成为目标并被打死，另一名男子向士兵投掷爆炸装置后被射杀。周三晚些时候，杰宁一家医院宣布第四名巴勒斯坦人因伤死亡</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 10:40:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/three-palestinians-killed-by-israeli-army-in-west-bank-two-of-them-in-airstrike/0000018e-7f52-d680-a1cf-ff57e8d30000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡与正统派的不正当联盟是他的又一失败之举</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-crooked-alliance-with-the-haredim-is-another-feather-of-failure-in-his-cap/0000018e-7cd8-d9f5-a7ae-7edd2ae00000</link><description>以色列总理对军队征召极端正统派人士的法律处理不当，包括拖延、投降和对形势的错误解读。照常。然而，这一次，他的犯罪同伙将首先受苦</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 04:00:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-crooked-alliance-with-the-haredim-is-another-feather-of-failure-in-his-cap/0000018e-7cd8-d9f5-a7ae-7edd2ae00000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡对唯一关心以色列利益的世界强国的令人困惑的蔑视</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-confounding-contempt-for-the-only-world-power-with-israels-interest-at-heart/0000018e-7c90-d680-a1cf-fe97200e0000</link><description>以色列完全依赖美国，但总理 — — 没有美国的批准，他什么也做不了 — — 却喋喋不休地谈论“全面胜利”。此外，美国对以色列的任何额外制裁都会对北方可能发生的战争产生影响</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 04:00:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-confounding-contempt-for-the-only-world-power-with-israels-interest-at-heart/0000018e-7c90-d680-a1cf-fe97200e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列对黎巴嫩的袭击造成至少八人死亡，其中包括真主党成员</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article-live/israeli-hostage-uriel-baruch-was-killed-on-oct-7-body-held-by-hamas-in-gaza-family-says/0000018e-7dc0-d680-a1cf-ffc7736c0000</link><description>以色列国防军公布了在加沙南部战斗中丧生的士兵的名字 ■ 哈马斯公布了军事部门负责人穆罕默德·德伊夫的录音，呼吁阿拉伯世界“向巴勒斯坦进军” ■ 白宫表示正在努力重新安排已取消的与以色列代表团就拉法选项举行的会议 ■ 以色列人在火箭中丧生袭击以色列北部</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 02:37:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article-live/israeli-hostage-uriel-baruch-was-killed-on-oct-7-body-held-by-hamas-in-gaza-family-says/0000018e-7dc0-d680-a1cf-ffc7736c0000</guid></item></channel></rss>